        <ul>
          <li>ROI: 20% website traffic increase (Sunrise Canada)</li>
          <li>Cost: Lower than traditional advertising</li>
          <li>Authenticity: High trust factor</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><strong>UGC Strategy:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li>28% higher engagement than brand posts</li>
          <li>50% more influence on purchasing decisions</li>
          <li>Tactics: Photo contests, event shares, testimonial incentives</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>
