      <li><strong>Q1:</strong> Partner with 2-3 local granfluencers in Michigan/Florida</li>
      <li><strong>Q2:</strong> Expand TikTok/Reels with short-form resident stories (&lt;60 seconds)</li>
      <li><strong>Ongoing:</strong> Invest in paid social to grow follower base (target: 15K+ by EOY)</li>
      <li><strong>Budget:</strong> $5K-$10K/month for influencer partnerships + paid amplification</li>
    </ul>
