<div class="section">
  <h1 class="slide-title">4. Decision-Maker Journey Mapping</h1>
  <p class="slide-subtitle">Search behavior, conversion metrics, and family priorities</p>
  
  <div class="data-grid">
    <div class="data-point highlighted">
      <span class="data-value">80%</span>
