      <span class="data-label">Inquiry to Move-In</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <h2 class="section-title">Journey Stages</h2>
  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>1. Awareness (Research)</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Google search: "senior living [city]", "assisted living near me"</li>
        <li>Aggregator sites: <strong>A Place for Mom, Caring.com dominate</strong></li>
        <li>80% of inquiries start digitally</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>2. Consideration (Tours)</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Families visit <strong>3 communities on average</strong></li>
        <li>Multiple tours per site (69% first tours)</li>
        <li>Virtual tours now standard</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>3. Decision (Move-In)</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>25-46 touchpoints</strong> required</li>
        <li><strong>80-106 days</strong> average timeline</li>
        <li>Shortened by proactive follow-ups</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  
