    <p><strong>86% of searches initiated by families</strong> (vs. 55% seniors). Marketing must address both audiences:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Families:</strong> Emphasize safety, staff quality, transparency</li>
      <li><strong>Seniors:</strong> Emphasize independence, lifestyle, value</li>
    </ul>
