      <li><strong>Tour booking:</strong> Calendar-based scheduling (64% booking increase benchmark)</li>
      <li><strong>Content:</strong> "Family Guide to Senior Living Decisions" hub</li>
      <li><strong>Retargeting:</strong> Multi-channel nurturing (email, SMS, social) for 25+ touchpoints</li>
